<Defs>

 <ScenarioDef> <!-- Quantum Mishap -->
		<defName>QuantumMishap</defName>
		<label>Quantum Mishap</label>
		<description>You and your colleagues tried to teleport yourselves to a set marker to showcase your groundbreaking teleportation technology and what it can do.
But...instead you teleported yourselves to a new world! Or is it the same one in another dimension? Or a different time? Who knows, but do you know if you can survive?!
-Classic SciFi gone wrong Tale-</description>
		<scenario>
		<summary>Teleporter test goes wrong, now you colleagues are stuck in a new world!</summary>
		<playerFaction>
			<def>PlayerFaction</def>
			<factionDef>PlayerColony</factionDef>
		</playerFaction>
		<parts>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ConfigPage_ConfigureStartingPawns">
				<def>ConfigPage_ConfigureStartingPawns</def>
				<pawnChoiceCount>4</pawnChoiceCount>
				<pawnCount>4</pawnCount>
