				<quality>Good</quality>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
				<def>StartingThing_Defined</def>
				<thingDef>Apparel_Pants</thingDef>
				<stuff>Hyperweave</stuff>
				<count>4</count>
				<quality>Good</quality>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ScatterThingsNearPlayerStart">
				<def>ScatterThingsNearPlayerStart</def>
				<thingDef>MedicineIndustrial</thingDef>
				<count>5</count>
				<allowRoofed>True</allowRoofed>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ScatterThingsNearPlayerStart">
				<def>ScatterThingsNearPlayerStart</def>
				<thingDef>Gun_BoltActionRifle</thingDef>
				<quality>Poor</quality>
				<allowRoofed>True</allowRoofed>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ScatterThingsAnywhere">
				<def>ScatterThingsAnywhere</def>
				<thingDef>Steel</thingDef>
				<count>400</count>
				<allowRoofed>True</allowRoofed>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ScatterThingsAnywhere">
				<def>ScatterThingsAnywhere</def>
				<thingDef>Gun_HeavySMG</thingDef>
				<count>2</count>
				<quality>Poor</quality>
				<allowRoofed>True</allowRoofed>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ScatterThingsAnywhere">
				<def>ScatterThingsAnywhere</def>
				<thingDef>MedicineIndustrial</thingDef>
				<count>20</count>
				<allowRoofed>True</allowRoofed>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_CreateIncident">
				<def>CreateIncident</def>
				<incident>TravelerGroup</incident>
				<intervalDays>10</intervalDays>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_CreateIncident">
				<def>CreateIncident</def>
				<incident>RefugeePodCrash</incident>
				<intervalDays>20</intervalDays>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_PawnFilter_Age">
				<def>PawnFilter_Age</def>
				<allowedAgeRange>15~19</allowedAgeRange>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_SetNeedLevel">
				<def>SetNeedLevel</def>
				<chance>0.8</chance>
				<context>PlayerStarter</context>
				<need>Mood</need>
				<levelRange>0.2874073~0.4711114</levelRange>
			</li>
		</parts>
	</scenario>
	</ScenarioDef>

<ScenarioDef> <!-- Stars Align For Us -->
		<defName>StarsAlignForUs</defName>
		<label>Stars Align For Us</label>
		<description>After a nice dinner you and your lover make your way home. A home you'll never see as you cross paths with a serial killer. Stabbing both you and your lover; you both lay their bleeding out under the stars.
By circumstance you both making the same request to the universe; gazing upon the same star. The universe has awarded both of you this request, and placed you upon a world orbiting the star you gazed on.
How will you both spend your days now? Together you remain after a cruel fate; will you survive or simply waste away this chance?
- A Tragic Lover's Tale-</description>
	<scenario>
	<summary>You and your lover are killed in cold blood. But you both make a final request to the universe; to keep you together. Now you're tossed into this new life; how will you spend it?</summary>
		<playerFaction>
			<def>PlayerFaction</def>
			<factionDef>PlayerColony</factionDef>
		</playerFaction>
		<parts>
			<li Class="ScenPart_ConfigPage_ConfigureStartingPawns">
				<def>ConfigPage_ConfigureStartingPawns</def>
				<pawnChoiceCount>2</pawnChoiceCount>
				<pawnCount>2</pawnCount>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_PlayerPawnsArriveMethod">
				<def>PlayerPawnsArriveMethod</def>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_GameStartDialog">
				<def>GameStartDialog</def>
				<text>Lover 1: Agh! We're not...we're not dying? Did my wish come true?!

Lover 2: Did you wish to stay together too?

Lover 1: Exactly!

Lover 2: The universe kept us together; truly a happier ending than...dying...

Lover 1: But where are we? Is this place safe? 

Lover 2: I would assume it's dangerous and we're alone.

Lover 1: At least we have each other...let's build a new home together.

Lover 2: That sounds like a lovely idea!</text>
			</li>
			<li Class="ScenPart_StartingThing_Defined">
